org.javasimon.utils

Class StopwatchAggregate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.javasimon.utils.StopwatchAggregate

  • public class StopwatchAggregate
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds aggregate values for stopwatches in a hierarchy as a result of SimonUtils.calculateStopwatchAggregate(Simon) (optionally with SimonFilter).
    Since:
    3.5
    Author:
    Ivan Mushketyk
